Use the standard library
This is how to mean_absolute_deviation of numbers:
   Remember that n is numbers's length
   Remember that total is tofloat of 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that x is item i in numbers
      Remember that total is sum of total and x
      Increase i
   End do
   Remember that mean is quotient of total and (tofloat of n)
   Remember that sum_dev is tofloat of 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that x is item i in numbers
      Remember that dev is abs of (diff of x and mean)
      Remember that sum_dev is sum of sum_dev and dev
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is quotient of sum_dev and (tofloat of n)
Now you know